 data-sentry-source-file="Spacer.tsx"></div><section class="container"><div class="row feature-item" data-sentry-component="Feature" data-sentry-source-file="Feature.tsx"><div class="col-md-6 mt-3 my-lg-auto position-relative order-md-first"><i class="fal fa-play-circle feature-icon text-focus fa-2x"></i><h2>Auto-translation</h2><p>Translate your application into multiple languages with just a few clicks. Choose from <strong>OpenAI ChatGPT</strong>, <strong>Google Translate</strong> or <strong>DeepL</strong> translation providers to translate your texts. Adding support for new languages has never been easier.</p><a href="/docs/general/auto-translation/" class="d-flex justify-content-start align-items-baseline">Learn more about auto-translation<i class="far fa-arrow-right ms-2"></i> </a></div><div class="col-md-6 mt-3 my-lg-auto order-md-last"><div class="BrowserWindow_container__stEPC" data-sentry-component="BrowserWindow" data-sentry-source-file="BrowserWindow.tsx"><div class="BrowserWindow_navigationBar__XDfud"><div class="d-flex justify-content-start align-items-center"><div class="BrowserWindow_navigationButton__OBbfa"></div><div class="BrowserWindow_navigationButton__OBbfa"></div><div class="BrowserWindow_navigationButton__OBbfa"></div></div></div><div><img src="/screenshots/auto-translation-tab.png" alt="Auto-translation tab in SimpleLocalize" title="Auto-translation tab in SimpleLocalize" class="img-fluid rounded-0 undefined"/></div></div></div></div><div class="row feature-item" data-sentry-component="Feature" data-sentry-source-file="Feature.tsx"><div class="col-md-6 mt-3 my-lg-auto position-relative order-md-last"><i class="fal fa-language feature-icon text-focus fa-2x"></i><h2>Translation Editor</h2><p>Online translation editor that helps you to manage your translations in one place. With numerous features like auto-translation, comments, and notifications, you can easily collaborate with your team and keep your translations up to date.</p><a href="/translation-editor/" class="d-flex justify-content-start align-items-baseline">See translation editor features<i class="far fa-arrow-right ms-2"></i> </a></div><div class="col-md-6 mt-3 my-lg-auto order-md-first"><div class="BrowserWindow_container__stEPC" data-sentry-component="BrowserWindow" data-sentry-source-file="BrowserWindow.tsx"><div class="BrowserWindow_navigationBar__XDfud"><div class="d-flex justify-content-start align-items-center"><div class="BrowserWindow_navigationButton__OBbfa"></div><div class="BrowserWindow_navigationButton__OBbfa"></div><div class="BrowserWindow_navigationButton__OBbfa"></div></div></div><div><img src="/screenshots/translation-editor--list-view.png" alt="SimpleLocalize Translation Editor" title="SimpleLocalize Translation Editor" class="img-fluid rounded-0 undefined"/></div></div></div></div><div class="row feature-item" data-sentry-component="Feature" data-sentry-source-file="Feature.tsx"><div class="col-md-6 mt-3 my-lg-auto position-relative order-md-first"><i class="fal fa-terminal feature-icon text-focus fa-2x"></i><h2>Command-line tool</h2><p>With SimpleLocalize CLI you can manage your translations from the terminal. It&#x27;s a powerful tool that helps you to automate the translation process in your project. You can easily synchronize translation files between you local project and SimpleLocalize Translation Editor, start auto-translation or publish changes to the production environment.</p><a href="/docs/cli/get-started/" class="d-flex justify-content-start align-items-baseline">CLI documentation<i class="far fa-arrow-right ms-2"></i> </a></div><div class="col-md-6 mt-3 my-lg-auto order-md-last"><div class="BrowserWindow_container__stEPC" data-sentry-component="BrowserWindow" data-sentry-source-file="BrowserWindow.tsx"><div class="BrowserWindow_navigationBar__XDfud"><div class="d-flex justify-content-start align-items-center"><div class="BrowserWindow_navigationButton__OBbfa"></div><div class="BrowserWindow_navigationButton__OBb